    description: 'Indiana limestone pavers are the perfect choice for many outdoor spaces — prized for their timeless beauty and ability to weather well while maintaining reliable traction even in wet conditions. Limestone pavers are low maintenance, long-lasting, and offer the perfect marriage of modern clean lines with traditional natural materials. Available in a variety of colours, cuts, and textures to suit any project.',
    benefits: [
      { title: 'Weather Resistant', body: 'Low-maintenance in Canadian climate' },
      { title: 'Natural Traction',  body: 'Safe in wet conditions year-round' },
      { title: 'Timeless Beauty',   body: 'Colour deepens gracefully with age' },
